    <item>
      <title>Sōzu 1.0.5 is available and deployed</title>
      <link>https://lafillepassympa.com/developers/changelog/2024-10-17-sozu-1.0.5/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://lafillepassympa.com/developers/changelog/2024-10-17-sozu-1.0.5/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.sozu.io&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Sōzu&lt;/a&gt; 1.0.5 is now available and deployed on &lt;code&gt;cleverapps.io&lt;/code&gt; domains, we&amp;rsquo;re progressively rolling it out on our own domains and dedicated load balancers. Since &lt;a href=&#34;https://lafillepassympa.com/developers/changelog/2024-10-04-sozu-1.0.2/&#34; &gt;the release of Sōzu 1.0.2&lt;/a&gt; we&amp;rsquo;ve fixed some bugs, improved CLI, metrics and performances.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&amp;rsquo;re currently testing the 1.1.0 release candidate of Sōzu, with HTTP/2 support, coming soon on Clever Cloud.&lt;/p&gt;
