&lt;li&gt;Learn more about &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/sozu-proxy/sozu/releases&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Sōzu new releases&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;hx-inline-block hx-align-text-bottom icon&#34;&gt;&lt;svg height=1em fill=&#34;currentColor&#34; viewBox=&#34;3 3 18 18&#34;&gt;
