    <item>
      <title>Montreal region (MTL): A records update for your domains/DNS</title>
      <link>https://lafillepassympa.com/developers/changelog/2024-02-26-mtl-iplb-update/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://lafillepassympa.com/developers/changelog/2024-02-26-mtl-iplb-update/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;As we&amp;rsquo;re upgrading our infrastructure and load balancers in Montreal, we&amp;rsquo;ve added new failover IPs in this region.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you configure your domains through CNAME records, this update will be transparent. But if you use A records, switch to CNAME or update your &lt;a href=&#34;https://developers.clever-cloud.com/doc/administrate/domain-names/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;DNS configuration&lt;/a&gt;. Old IPs will continue to work for a while, but we recommend you to update your DNS as soon as possible to avoid any service interruption.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Applications&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;applications&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#applications&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;table&gt;
